This paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes the use of Genetic Programming to evolve Gaussian Process kernels for sentiment analysis. Additionally, the paper also involves the use of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) techniques for improving the precision of sentiment analysis. The paper also deals with Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it involves the analysis of text for sentiment. Neural Networks (cs.NE) and Software Engineering (cs.SE) could also be possible sub-categories as the paper involves the use of computational techniques for improving the performance of sentiment analysis.
